title: Monthly Border Crossings into the US, January-July 2009
name: Monthly Border Crossings into the US, January-July 2009
description: Incoming monthly border crossing/entry data for vehicles, containers, passengers and pedestrians. The data represents activity at the port level on the U.S.-Canadian and U.S.-Mexican land border and international ferry crossings. The data is provided to BTS by the U.S. Department of Homeland Security - Customs and Border Protection.
